      "Brown onion slowly like you're caramalizing (important)",
      "Add garlic once onions brown so as to not burn",
      "Add tomato puree and reduce, you want to bring out the sweetness",
      "Add stock and herbs but not bay leaf",
      "Add first can of beans and puree with immersion blender",
      "Add bay leaf and simmer ~30 min",
      "When almost done add the other can of beans",
      "Toast hazlenuts then chop; sprinkle on top or mix with chopped parsley and olive oil and add on top"
