    "directions": [
      "Sear mushrooms in batchs on med-high heat in butter and oil",
      "Very important to not steam them, they need to caramalize; All the flavour is built here",
      "(Optional) Reserve some for garnish",
      "Add onion and celery until translucent; Add garlic after",
      "Deglaze with wine/sherry au sec",
      "Add stock and herbs; Simmer 12-15 min",
      "Add cream; Remove stems/rind; Blend smooth",
      "Add a splash of sherry vinegar"
    ],
